依赖：
tpm-tss
https://github.com/tpm2-software/tpm2-tss
gmp: sudo apt install libgmp-dev
flex: sudo apt install flex
bison: sudo apt install bison
pbc: https://crypto.stanford.edu/pbc/download.html  下载pbc-1.0.0.tar.gz
$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install
再添加路径
echo "/usr/local/lib" | sudo tee /etc/ld.so.conf.d/pbc.conf
pbc安装参考：https://crypto.stanford.edu/pbc/manual/ch01.html

Infineon SLB9670的TPM在树莓派的配置
sudo raspi-config
进入 Interfacing Options -> SPI -> Enable，然后 重启

sudo nano /boot/config.txt
在最后一行加上  dtoverlay=tpm-slb9670

重启

ls /dev/tpm*
查看是否有设备存在


